<p>$Q_0^+=\overline{Q_0}$</p>

<h4 id="驱动器方程">驱动器方程</h4>

<p>$J_3=Q_2Q_1Q_0,K_3=Q_2$</p>

<p>$J_2=Q_1Q_0,K_2=\overline{\overline{Q_3}(\overline{Q_1}+\overline{Q_0})}=Q_3+Q_1Q_0$</p>

<p>$J_1=K_1=Q_0$</p>

<p>$J_0=K_0=1$</p>

